 physical constraints in\nthe encoder-decoder architectures, and generative physical laws, topological\ninvariances, and causal relationships in the latent space of VAEs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Oct 2020 03:53:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 13 Apr 2021 05:57:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-14"}
