observations throughout the wall\nlayer. The dissipation characteristics in this very near wall region show that\n$\\varepsilon_{ij}$ is close to but different from $\\mathcal{D}_{ij}$ .\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Oct 2020 09:29:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-20"}
